<!-- How to Use This db.json:
Replace your existing db.json with this content or create a new db.json file in your project folder.
Start the json-server:
bash
Copy code
json-server --watch db.json --port 3000
This will serve the cocktail data at http://localhost:3000/cocktails.
API Endpoints:
GET all cocktails: http://localhost:3000/cocktails
GET a specific cocktail: http://localhost:3000/cocktails/:id


